}}'''Uganda''' is a [[Nations|country]] that was added to [[BitLife: Life Simulator|BitLife]] in July 10, 2022.

On July 10, 2022, new countries were added to both iOS and Android. Along with Uganda, there was also [[Andorra]], [[Angola]], [[Aruba]], [[Belize]], [[El Salvador]], [[Guatemala]], [[Guyana]], [[Haiti]], [[Nicaragua]], [[Papua New Guinea]], [[Paraguay]], [[Samoa]], and [[Tunisia]]. This was added in a bug fix update prior to the upcoming Business Update.

